{
  "texts": [
    "See Appendix G for more details.",
    "LOCALRQA supports a large variety of models and training algorithms.",
    "To demonstrate the flexibility of our toolkit, we experiment with all available trainers and the most capable open-source models.",
    "Retrievers We consider the best open-source encoder models according to the MTEB benchmark (Muennighoff et al., 2022) as of Jan 24, 2024.",
    "However, as these models vary greatly in capability and size, for simplicity we use the best models of similar sizes."
  ]
}